#, php-format
msgid "Add a Smart AI Chatbot to Your %s Site"
msgstr "为你的 %s 网站添加智能 AI 聊天机器人"

#: front-page.php:9
msgid ""
"ChatBudgie uses RAG technology to answer users based on your website "
"content. Easy to use, private by design, and built for WordPress."
msgstr ""
"ChatBudgie 使用 RAG 技术，根据你的网站内容回答用户问题。简单易用，注重隐私，"
"专为 WordPress 打造。"

#: front-page.php:11 front-page.php:126
msgid "Download Plugin"
msgstr "下载插件"

#: front-page.php:18
msgid "View on GitHub"
msgstr "在 GitHub 上查看"

#: front-page.php:29 front-page.php:41 front-page.php:53
msgid "Feature"
msgstr "功能"

#: front-page.php:30
msgid "Smart Chat"
msgstr "智能聊天"

#: front-page.php:31
msgid "Answers from your content, not the internet."
msgstr "答案来自你的网站内容，而不是整个互联网。"

#: front-page.php:32
msgid ""
"ChatBudgie understands your website content using RAG technology and gives "
"accurate, context-aware answers to your visitors."
msgstr ""
"ChatBudgie 使用 RAG 技术理解你的网站内容，为访客提供准确且结合上下文的回答。"

#: front-page.php:42
msgid "Easy to Setup"
msgstr "轻松设置"

#: front-page.php:43
msgid "Get started in just a few minutes."
msgstr "只需几分钟即可开始使用。"

#: front-page.php:44
msgid ""
"Don't need to set up various API keys. ChatBudgie will manage it for you."
msgstr "无需配置各种 API 密钥。ChatBudgie 会为你处理。"

#: front-page.php:54
msgid "Zero Maintenance"
msgstr "零维护"

#: front-page.php:55
msgid "Set it up and let it work for you."
msgstr "完成设置后，它会自动为你工作。"

#: front-page.php:56
msgid ""
"ChatBudgie automatically keeps your knowledge base up to date. No manual "
"work, no server management, no headaches."
msgstr ""
"ChatBudgie 会自动保持知识库最新。无需手动操作，无需管理服务器，也没有额外烦"
"恼。"

